thread.title: Lee & Karolina
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Lee & Karolina

author: Lee & Karolina
title: Lee & Karolina
text: We are immensely grateful to Michelle Portelli and her team at Nelson Alexander's Preston branch for another wonderful selling experience. Michelle's unwavering commitment to the campaign, her proactivity and knowledge of the market were second to none. We would not hesitate to recommend Michelle's team to any seller looking for engaged real estate professionals who conduct themselves with integrity before, during and after the date of sale.
